{"tid":1024838,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國債爆表！　鄉民神建議：賣掉蒙大拿州 Montana","createTime":"2019-02-17T01:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T01:30:55.000Z","uid":141151,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e3b8bf1c3f13b256390265779b6c70983d6468d0","tid":1024838,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T01:03:49.000Z","msg":"美國債爆表！　鄉民神建議：賣掉蒙大拿州<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190216/1517918/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190216%2F1517918%2F&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7Ly8lxPyN12Ak3mY6G5vlvHI%3D&h=6d4192a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190216%2F1517918%2F&h=0370ec2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190216/1517918/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國債日前已突破22兆美元（約678兆台幣），有美國鄉民想出另類還債法，建議「賣領土」，嘲諷不斷舉債的美國政府。<a href=\"http://美網站change.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%BE%8E%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99change.org&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7Ly8lxPyN12Ak3mY6G5vlvHI%3D&h=9b0d8189\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">美網站change.org</a>近日發動請願，希望將毗鄰加拿大的蒙大拿州以1兆美元（約30.8兆台幣）賣掉，以減輕國債負擔。<br />\n<br />\n《赫芬頓郵報》報導，這個請願名稱是「減輕國債，蒙大拿州1兆美元賣加拿大。」發起人哈蒙德（Ian Hammond）表示：「我們債務太多，而蒙大拿州毫無用處，只有河貍之類的。」有趣的是，河狸在加拿大是國寶級的動物。<br />\n<br />\n請願目前已積累了超過4700人簽名，並且持續增加。儘管乍看有點荒唐滑稽，但不少美國網友都提出理由，支持賣掉蒙大拿州；有人認為該州人口微不足道，就算領土賣掉，當地人也可以轉移到其他州。<br />\n<br />\n連住在蒙大拿的人似乎也同意這想法。1位評論者說：「我認為這對所有人都好，我在加拿大有親戚，瞭解當加拿大人的好處。」另1名蒙大拿人則說：「我這輩子都在這生活。坦白說，我厭倦美國對人類生命的漠視。」<br />\n<br />\n許多支持請願的美國網友，甚至建議連其它州也賣掉。有人說：「也賣掉沒人關心的懷俄明和愛達荷州吧。」「加州如何...那裡的野火一直在製造債務。」<br />\n<br />\n但現實而言，這個請願成真的可能性不高。依據美國憲法，聯邦政府出售任何1州的難度都很高，因為這可能牴觸憲法第10修正案中各州擁有自決權的法案。<br />\n<br />\n（吳國仲╱綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n======網友看法======<br />\n有網友開玩笑說，賣給中華民國好了，台灣房價真得太貴。"},{"pid":"f75e81302e35a69945377dc596552bde47a50c9f","tid":1024838,"uid":18395,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T01:06:42.000Z","msg":"中共會用2兆買"},{"pid":"246f73338dc9ee916c8ea4915edd6073af2d0cdd","tid":1024838,"uid":191338,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T01:12:29.000Z","msg":"香港人夾錢買"},{"pid":"cf469c5e87c7f810fcf744d6a5e9bf40751f9a88","tid":1024838,"uid":121146,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T01:12:44.000Z","msg":"要賣都賣加州啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579808022afcb6ac8f9ad2eb1a03748e4399ed65","tid":1024838,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T01:16:27.000Z","msg":"擺明係某d人想移加拿大+某國既力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553956339403375c4b064bd7c0b2cf3e0bc96e72","tid":1024838,"uid":145277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T01:17:52.000Z","msg":"聯儲局縮表+唔印銀紙就會咁架啦<br />\n<br />\n不過啊森家族估中晒😂"},{"pid":"4cfcb6e87acb2d50d1cab53f179ce539a5c6bc3a","tid":1024838,"uid":170244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"246f73338dc9ee916c8ea4915edd6073af2d0cdd","tid":1024838,"uid":191338,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T01:12:29.000Z","msg":"香港人夾錢買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T01:19:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞眾籌舉腳贊成"},{"pid":"4a0b24ffcad5eb77ac8c8ba20e059154f47de487","tid":1024838,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"246f73338dc9ee916c8ea4915edd6073af2d0cdd","tid":1024838,"uid":191338,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T01:12:29.000Z","msg":"香港人夾錢買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T01:21:55.000Z","msg":"明日蒙大拿"},{"pid":"8d875849a386d29e104393d454876131e2e15a70","tid":1024838,"uid":8257,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf469c5e87c7f810fcf744d6a5e9bf40751f9a88","tid":1024838,"uid":121146,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T01:12:44.000Z","msg":"要賣都賣加州啦<img src=\"/assets/fac